# ============================================================================
# Terraform
# ============================================================================
terraform/*.tfstate
terraform/*.tfstate.*
terraform/*.tfvars
!terraform/terraform.tfvars.example
terraform/.terraform/
terraform/.terraform.lock.hcl
terraform/crash.log
tfplan
*.tfplan

# ============================================================================
